I"E<p><strong>Employer Awareness and Education Web Sites</strong>
 The sites below are all focused on providing employers with practical info, fact sheets, and resources to dispel myths, and promote recruitment, hiring, and retention of employees with disabilities.</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="http://www.askearn.org/">The Employer Assistance and Resource Network on Disability Inclusion (EARN)</a></li>
  <li><a href="http://www.shrm.org/hrdisciplines/Diversity/Articles/Pages/disability_072110.aspx">Disability Employment Resource Page</a></li>
  <li><a href="http://www.dol.gov/odep/topics/RecruitmentAndRetention.htm">Recruitment and Retention (ODEP)</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://icdr.acl.gov/system/files/resources/survey_report_jan_09.pdf">Survey of Employer Perspectives on the
Employment of People with Disabilities </a></li>
</ul>
